<% content_for(:title, "About - Brooke & Maisy Interior Designs") %>

<section class="bg-theme-100 py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-theme-500 mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -1px;">Our Story</h1>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          At Brooke & Maisy Interior Designs, we believe your home should feel beautiful, welcoming, and completely you. We love creating spaces that are polished but still comfortable, stylish but still livable, and thoughtfully designed for real life, pets, kids, coffee cups, cozy blankets, and all. Honestly, this is my fire. I'm Amanda Nelson, the owner of Brooke & Maisy Interior Design. I've been a hobbyist designer for the better part of a decade, but now the credentials are solid, so I decided to give into that fire and make this gift a full time business.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our company was named after two very special girls: Brooke and Maisy. Brooke, our sweet and loyal Corgi, brings the heart, happiness, and playful energy behind everything we do. She reminds us that a home should feel safe, warm, and full of joy. She inspires me, and thus is the best kind of helper. Maisy, our beautiful calico cat, brings the charm, personality, and a little bit of sass, because every great design needs a touch of character. She keeps me level and reminds me that sometimes my “design-crazy” needs to be reeled in. In other words, she keeps me grounded.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-4/3 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border-4 border-theme-300 p-1 bg-white shadow-xl">
        <%= image_tag "Brooke-and-Maisy-and-Mom.png", alt: "Amanda - Brooke & Maisy Interior Designs", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Together, Brooke and Maisy represent what we want every client to feel when they work with us: comfort, creativity, trust, and a whole lot of love. One of the most important things for me is to be budget friendly. I've gotten the three quotes so you don't have to. My car is a mobile showroom, and we have the availability to make all the things happen. Together, lets create something really, really beautiful.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Whether we are helping you refresh one room, choose the perfect finishes, style your shelves, select window treatments, or pull together a full design plan, our goal is simple: to make the process feel exciting instead of overwhelming.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      We believe design should be approachable, personal, and fun. Your home tells your story, and we would be honored to make you say “yeah... it's finished now”. And other astonishing words I probably can't post on a company bio.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      Brooke & Maisy Interior Designs</br>
      Thoughtful spaces. Happy homes. A little personality in every detail.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Contact CTA %>
<section class="bg-theme-500 text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -1px;">Let's create something beautiful</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Book a free 30-minute consultation to discuss your project — no pressure, just a conversation about your vision.
    </p>
    <%= link_to "Book a Free Consultation", contact_path,
          class: "inline-block bg-theme-400 hover:bg-theme-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition-colors" %>
  </div>
</section>